{"tid":740958,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人睇過《致命中國》本書","createTime":"2018-07-13T09:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T04:01:22.000Z","uid":28765,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3277ac88ccc1b98aa907a4302a7056a8243584dd","tid":740958,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:35:50.000Z","msg":"睇完覺得好黑暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本書講到中國已經全方位（經濟/軍力）對美國造成 <br />\n<br />\n嚴重威脅<br />\n<br />\n雖然書入面有d問題：北韓，工商業最近有小小改善<br />\n<br />\n但仍然好擔心中國對世界既威脅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似中國將非洲變成殖民地，再壟斷全世界既金屬資源<br />\n<br />\n美國最自豪既工業力量，因為經濟因素美國轉移到<br />\n中國<br />\n<br />\n美國即使現時軍力上有優勢，但中國由剽竊，間諜盜取後再發展既技術，軍備<br />\n<br />\n就算質素較差亦足以淹沒美軍<br />\n<br />\n仲有大量針對性發展既不對等武裝<br />\n<br />\n睇完本書真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95181d8c4f4238a021939fecd361f02699b7cb88","tid":740958,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:43:55.000Z","msg":"Wargaming, including an extensive simulation by Rand, has shown that the U.S. would generate a 6-1 kill ratio over Chinese aircraft, but the Americans would lose.<br />\n<br />\n本書寫既蘭德公司分析美國殺敵率6:1優於中國戰機，但美國最終都會戰敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog.usni.org/posts/2011/01/12/chinese-air-force-could-overwhelm-opponents\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.usni.org%2Fposts%2F2011%2F01%2F12%2Fchinese-air-force-could-overwhelm-opponents&d=qbA0rtXWdwE9mYCSP4H%2BOzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=d986e74e\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.usni.org/posts/2011/01/12/chinese-air-force-could-overwhelm-opponents</a>"},{"pid":"cccfa5e4da0d1a4122798e14ab76325be12b2846","tid":740958,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":2,